1.1.1.1
log
@Initial import of ruby-id3lib-0.5.0.

id3lib-ruby provides a Ruby interface to the id3lib C++ library for
easily editing ID3 tags (v1 and v2) of MP3 audio files.

Submitted and maintained by Paul Irofti.
